<template>
    <v-container fluid fill-height>
      <v-row align="center" justify="center">
        <v-col cols="12" sm="8" md="6" lg="5" xl="4">
          <v-card>
            <v-toolbar dark color="red darken-1">
              <v-toolbar-title>Inicio de sesi칩n</v-toolbar-title>
            </v-toolbar>
            <v-card-text>
              <v-text-field
                color="accent"
                label="Usuario"
                class="login"
                required
              ></v-text-field>
              <v-text-field
                :append-icon="show ? 'mdi-eye' : 'mdi-eye-off'"
                color="accent"
                label="Contrase침a"
                :type="show ? 'text' : 'password'"
                @click:append="show = !show"
                required
                @keyup.enter="ingresar"
              ></v-text-field>
            </v-card-text>
            <v-card-actions class="px-3 pb-3">
              <v-spacer></v-spacer>
              <v-btn  color="primary">Ingresar</v-btn>
            </v-card-actions>
          </v-card>
        </v-col>
      </v-row>
    </v-container>
  </template>

</script>
